body:
I was playing a rank game as {{champion:1}} , and my ping shot up to 142 and stayed there. The entire game my actions were delayed - I couldn't even ult because by the time my ult went off everyone was far away. I don't have Verizon, I have buckeye cable. My ping is usually always 26-27 - I NEVER lag since I pay for the highest speed internet in the area.

I already ran the Hextech Repair Tool, and checked my ping/internet. It's not any of my stuff.

Riot, you really need to fix this ASAP, you're servers are costing people ranked games. {{sticker:sg-ahri-3}}
